al/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c473a3af81d5dacdd3a07ffa8d9b8a5c567d44","tid":2411271,"uid":143526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f9ce3fc78e7681335cf84e2c316aefbf90e5d0d","tid":2411271,"uid":402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:54:05.000Z","msg":"做總統都唔敢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c4f41d0eaa1acbbc25bdfeae5c9705f64a937c","tid":2411271,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:56:04.000Z","msg":"香港海外研究生民主聯盟成員、<span class=\"red\">加州大學爾灣分校社會學博士生 - 莫哲暐</span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>最後我要說：我接納自己會錯，也願意認錯。如果1月20日Trump真的連任，並拘捕「叛國者」；<span class=\"red\">如果Biden上任4年後，美國真的變成中國的一個省，而台灣真的被武統；那麼，我願意認錯，公開承受眾人批判。</span>這就是我和袁爸爸、吳嘉隆、陶傑，甚至王丹的分別。我膽敢再下一個判斷：香港不會因為Trump下台而消亡。因為香港的反抗精神，從來都不是靠一群狂熱Trump粉、靠哄騙愚弄搵食的KOL，以及在道德危機前和稀泥「菠蘿雞」的「中立」人士。香港的未來，從來是靠一群勇敢、有智慧，並願意堅持原則的人（利申：不包括我）。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n莫狗fb: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/IoanneMok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FIoanneMok&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN27vH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=03481cb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/IoanneMok</a><br />\n<br />\n莫狗IG:<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/mokcwjohn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fmokcwjohn&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN27vH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=9b7b9dbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/mokcwjohn</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/ivorytower_hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%